<p>The trend for posts per year is looking encouraging when looking at the past decade, here’s to a few more (while computers <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Year_2038_problem" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">still work</a>).</p>